import React from 'react'
import './Search.css'

function Search() {
  return (
    <form className='searchForm' onSubmit={(e)=>e.preventDefault()}>
        <input
            id='search'
            type='text'
            placeholder='Enter search string here...'
            role='searchbox'
        />    
    </form>
  )
}

export default Search
